"Milk is reconstituted with water that has been previously boiled for at least 10 minutes. # Formula without ReSoMal\nIn the absence of both vitamin and mineral complements and ReSoMal, a formula similar to F-75 may nevertheless be prepared; it however lacks the amounts of vitamins and minerals that are necessary for the optimal treatment of severe malnutrition. The amount of sugar is increased to compensate for the absence of ReSoMal."